A1|title=洪素珠代班故事媽媽　不只1次是9次 {{!}} 即時新聞 {{!}} 20160611 {{!}} 蘋果日報|accessdate=2016-06-11|work=蘋果日報|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2016-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805014642/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/politics/20160611/883616/%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B4%25AA%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E7%258F%25A0%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%258F%25AD%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AA1%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E8%2580%258C%25E6%2598%25AF9%25E6%25AC%25A1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

